# Simple Banking Application (Core Java)

A basic console-based banking system developed using **Core Java**.  
This project demonstrates Java fundamentals such as OOP, encapsulation, methods, loops, and user input handling.

## Features
- Create Account
- Deposit Money
- Withdraw Money
- Check Balance
- Menu-driven Interface

## Concepts Used
- Classes & Objects
- Encapsulation
- Methods
- Conditional Logic
- Scanner Class
- Loops

